          </li>
        </ul>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="mr-2 w-5 h-5 mt-1 text-green">
              <use href="#icon-check"></use>
            </svg>
            <span><strong>BMS Compatibility</strong> – Integration with fire and building management systems.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="mr-2 w-5 h-5 mt-1 text-green">
              <use href="#icon-check"></use>
            </svg>
            <span><strong>Remote Access Monitoring</strong> – Cloud-based platforms for multi-site compliance.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-6">
