      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TESTING, MAINTENANCE & LEGAL DOCUMENTATION -->
  <section class="py-20 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-medium mb-6">Testing, Maintenance & Legal Documentation</h2>
      <p class="mb-6">We offer contract-based or ad-hoc maintenance services for emergency lighting, ensuring your systems are always compliant and operational:</p>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="mr-2 w-5 h-5 mt-1 text-green">
              <use href="#icon-check"></use>
            </svg>
            <span>Monthly function test (flick test) as part of emergency lighting testing</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="mr-2 w-5 h-5 mt-1 text-green">
              <use href="#icon-check"></use>
            </svg>
            <span>Annual 3-hour full duration test to verify battery capacity and system reliability</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="mr-2 w-5 h-5 mt-1 text-green">
              <use href="#icon-check"></use>
            </svg>
            <span>Battery replacement and fault diagnosis</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="mr-2 w-5 h-5 mt-1 text-green">
              <use href="#icon-check"></use>
            </svg>
            <span>Test key switch installation</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="mr-2 w-5 h-5 mt-1 text-green">
              <use href="#icon-check"></use>
            </svg>
            <span>Digital and paper logbooks</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
